                                "stop": 7.881,
                                "byte_start": 90841,
                                "byte_stop": 122397,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 90-7477, Smith against Barry will be announced by Justice O\u0027Connor."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 7.881,
                        "stop": 112.823,
